 Chaka Khan 的 Meltdown 2024 公布了名字https://www.nme.com/news/music/first-names-announced-for-chaka-khans-meltdown-2024-3602392?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=first-names-announced-for-chaka-khans-崩溃-2024Max Pilley Sun, 17 Mar 2024 21:33:07 +0000 FestivalsMusic NewsNewsLive Music NewsMeltdown FestivalSoul https://www.nme.com/?p=3602392 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/chaka_khan_2024.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="查卡汗" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/chaka_khan_2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/chaka_khan_2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/chaka_khan_2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/chaka_khan_2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/chaka_khan_2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/chaka_khan_2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>汗本人将在音乐节开幕日和闭幕日演奏两场</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/first-names-announced-for-chaka-khans-meltdown-2024-3602392">Chaka Khan 的《Meltdown 2024》公布名字的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/chaka_khan_2024.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="查卡汗" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/chaka_khan_2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/chaka_khan_2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/chaka_khan_2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/chaka_khan_2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/chaka_khan_2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/chaka_khan_2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>今年 6 月举行的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chaka-khan">Chaka Khan</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/meltdown-festival">熔断节</a>的首批名单已经公布。</p><p>一年一度的当代音乐节定于 6 月 14 日至 23 日举行， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chaka-khan-to-curate-meltdown-2024-to-celebrate-50-years-of-music-3578720">南岸中心 (Southbank Centre) 一月份确认</a>汗将策划今年的音乐节。</p><p> Khan 本人将在音乐节上表演两场演出，其中包括在皇家节日音乐厅开幕之夜表演的热门歌曲，以及在闭幕之夜表演她 2004 年的专辑《ClassiKhan》，届时她将与 Black-领导怒族文明乐团。 </p><figure id="attachment_3578722" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3578722" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3578722" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Chaka-Khan@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Chaka-Khan@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Chaka-Khan@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Chaka-Khan@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Chaka-Khan@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Chaka-Khan@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Chaka-Khan@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3578722" class="wp-caption-text"> Chaka Khan，2024。图片来源：Jo Metson Scott</figcaption></figure><p>同时宣布的还有 Brixton 爵士乐团音箱角四重奏 (Speakers Corner Quartet)、Lady Blackbird、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/morcheeba">Morcheeba</a> 、Mica Paris 和 Incognito。</p><p> “很荣幸能与大家分享一些杰出的艺术家，他们将庆祝 Meltdown 的多样性和遗产！”汗在一份新声明中说道。 “我们都是一家人。准备好唱歌、跳舞，感受爱！”</p><p> Khan 是第 29 位获得此殊荣的艺术家，这将庆祝她 50 年的职业生涯。 “这个音乐节不仅仅是音乐，更是一场所有感官的盛宴，一场心灵和灵魂的聚会，”她当时说道。</p><p> “南岸中心即将亮灯！我们将把它搞砸，震撼每一个人群，感动每一个灵魂。这是一场社区庆典，一场全年龄段的狂欢。加入我们，让自己沉浸在一个充满活力、多样化且绝对令人难忘的世界中。”</p><p>该音乐节距这位歌手 1978 年突破性的同名首张专辑《Chaka》45 周年，同时还获得了 10 项<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/grammys">格莱美</a>奖，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kate-bush-and-george-michael-are-among-2023-rock-roll-hall-of-fame-inductees-3438846">于去年入选摇滚名人堂</a>。</p><p> Meltdown 音乐节自 1993 年起每年举办一次，吸引了一些音乐界最知名人士的合作，其中包括前策展人大卫·<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/davis-bowie">鲍伊 (David Bowie)</a> 、罗伯特·史密斯 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/robert-smith">Robert Smith)</a> 、贾维斯·科克 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jarvis-cocker">Jarvis Cocker)、卢·里德</a>( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lou-reed">Lou Reed)</a> 、杰夫·贝克 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jeff-beck">Jeff Beck)</a>等。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/christine-and-the-queens-announced-as-meltdown-festival-2022-curator-3353676">去年的版本由 Christine And The Queens 策划</a>，并有<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sigur-ros">Sigur Rós</a> 、Yemi Alade、Johnny Jewel、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/warpaint">Warpaint</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lynks">Lynks</a>等人的表演。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/first-names-announced-for-chaka-khans-meltdown-2024-3602392">Chaka Khan 的《Meltdown 2024》公布名字的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
